# Results

This folder is populated automatically when you run `src/evaluate.py`
(or the Colab notebook in `notebooks/run_on_colab.ipynb`):

- `metrics_before.json` — zero-shot base model scores on the held-out test set
- `metrics_after.json` — LoRA fine-tuned model scores on the same test set
- `comparison.png` — bar chart comparing the two
- `sample_outputs.md` — a handful of real before/after example predictions

It's empty right now because these numbers need to come from an actual
training run on a GPU — nothing here is filled in with placeholder or
invented numbers. Run the pipeline (see the main README's "Getting started"
section), then replace this file's contents with your real results and
commit the generated files in this folder.
